com.orchestranetworks.d3
Interface D3Node

All Known Subinterfaces:
D3NodeAsMaster, D3NodeAsSlave
public interface D3Node

Represents the external view of the D3 engine and offers common administrative functionalities.

All methods are read-only and are used to retrieve the D3 node information.

Since:
5.4.2

Method Detail

getBroadcastVersion

VersionKey getBroadcastVersion(BranchKey aDataSpaceKey)
Returns the last broadcast snapshot for the specified data space key. The following conditions should be valid:
  • Corresponds to an open delivery data space.
  • Registered as a master or slave delivery data space.
  • Broadcasted at least once.

Otherwise a null is returned.

Parameters:
aDataSpaceKey - D3 data space key
Since:
5.4.2

getD3SlaveFromRepositoryId

D3Slave getD3SlaveFromRepositoryId(String aRepositoryId)
Returns the registered slave for the specified identifier.

If unknown in the master repository or if slave mode only, returns null.

Parameters:
aRepositoryId - remote slave repository ID.
Throws:
NullPointerException - if aRepositoryId is null.
Since:
5.5.1

getD3SlaveFromRepositoryLabel

getRegisteredSlaves

List getRegisteredSlaves(BranchKey aDataSpaceKey)
Returns the list of the D3Slave object(s) subscribed to the data space specified in the parameter.

The returned list is empty if in slave mode only or if no slave registered on this node.

Parameters:
aDataSpaceKey - D3 data space key.
Since:
5.5.1
